    <p>2 At Anouska’s Bar, the cock­tail you should ab­so­lutely not miss out on is Es­cape To Kaifeng ($24), a house­made chrysan­the­mum cor­dial with Tan­queray gin that achieves a star­tling clar­ity of flavour.</p>
    <p>3 De­sign your own cus­tomised scent at the ho­tel’s neigh­bour Mai­son 21G, which runs a be­spoke per­fume work­shop ($150 a per­son with a 15 per cent dis­count for ho­tel guests).</p>


